      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 3,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "my God is my rock, in whom I take refuge, my shield and the horn of my salvation. He is my stronghold, my refuge and my savior— from violent people you save me."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
